00:12:50,311 --> 00:12:52,647
Sorry, I thought we'd started.

246
00:12:52,689 --> 00:12:55,567
-Go to the back.
-Oh, dear.

247
00:12:55,609 --> 00:12:58,236
Always one, isn't there?

248
00:12:58,278 --> 00:13:00,113
Now, where were we?

249
00:13:00,154 --> 00:13:03,491
Look, I don't think
it ought to be blasphemy
just saying "Jehovah".

250
00:13:03,533 --> 00:13:05,159
-[angry shouting]
-[all shout in feminine
voices] He did it again!

251
00:13:05,201 --> 00:13:07,786
You're only making it
worse for yourself!

252
00:13:07,828 --> 00:13:10,582
Making it worse?!
How could it be worse?

253
00:13:10,624 --> 00:13:13,334
