255
00:13:17,297 --> 00:13:19,966
Right! Who threw that?

256
00:13:21,175 --> 00:13:22,636
Come on! Who threw that?

257
00:13:22,677 --> 00:13:24,721
[all shouting
in feminine voices]

258
00:13:24,763 --> 00:13:27,974
