in masculine voices]
Him! Him! Him!

259
00:13:28,015 --> 00:13:29,643
-Was it you?
-Yes.

260
00:13:29,684 --> 00:13:31,269
-Right--
-Well, you did say Jehovah.

261
00:13:31,311 --> 00:13:33,480
[high-pitched screaming]

262
00:13:35,440 --> 00:13:38,901
