Do you understand?

266
00:13:47,619 --> 00:13:50,789
Even, and I want to
make this absolutely clear,

267
00:13:50,829 --> 00:13:53,040
even if they do say "Jehovah"!

268
00:13:53,082 --> 00:13:54,917
[screaming resumes]

269
00:13:56,336 --> 00:13:59,673
