the Macedonian baby-crusher,

373
00:18:30,526 --> 00:18:33,654
and Boris Mineburg.

374
00:18:33,696 --> 00:18:35,949
[Brian] Thank you, madam.

375
00:18:35,990 --> 00:18:37,533
Larks' tongues.

376
00:18:37,575 --> 00:18:39,201
Wrens' livers.

377
00:18:39,243 --> 00:18:41,370
Chaffinch brains.

378
00:18:41,412 --> 00:18:43,623
Jaguars' earlobes.

379
00:18:43,664 --> 00:18:45,124
Wolf-nipple chips.

380
00:18:45,165 --> 00:18:46,500
Get them while they're hot.
They're lovely.

381
00:18:46,542 --> 00:18:49,003
Dromedary pretzels,
only half a dinar.

382
00:18:49,045 --> 00:18:50,630
Tuscany fried bats...

383
00:18:50,671 --> 00:18:54,050
I do feel, Reg, that any
anti-imperialist group like ours

384
00:18:54,092 --> 00:18:58,137
