of view is very valid, Reg,

387
00:19:01,933 --> 00:19:03,726
provided the movement
never forgets

388
00:19:03,768 --> 00:19:06,145
that it is the unalienable
right of every man...

389
00:19:06,186 --> 00:19:08,397
-Or woman.
-...or woman, to rid himself...

390
00:19:08,439 --> 00:19:09,607
-Or herself.
-...or herself--

391
00:19:09,649 --> 00:19:10,817
-Agreed.
-Thank you, brother.

392
00:19:10,858 --> 00:19:12,944
-Or sister.
-Or sister...

393
00:19:14,070 --> 00:19:15,613
Where was I?

394
00:19:16,697 --> 00:19:17,740
I think you finished.

395
00:19:17,782 --> 00:19:19,366
Oh, right.

396
00:19:19,408 --> 00:19:21,368
Furthermore, it is the
birthright of every man...

397
00:19:21,410 --> 00:19:23,412
Or woman.

398
00:19:23,454 --> 00:19:25,331
Why don't you shut up
about women, Stan,
you're putting us off.

399
00:19:25,372 --> 00:19:28,084
Women have a perfect right
to play a part in our movement,
Reg.

400
00:19:28,126 --> 00:19:31,211
Why are you always
on about women, Stan?

401
00:19:31,253 --> 00:19:32,421
