the right to have babies.

419
00:20:22,221 --> 00:20:24,390
Good idea, Judith.

420
00:20:24,431 --> 00:20:27,351
We shall fight the oppressors
for your right to have babies,
brother--

421
00:20:27,393 --> 00:20:30,563
-Sister. Sorry.
-What's the point?

422
00:20:30,604 --> 00:20:32,606
-What?
-What's the point of fighting

423
00:20:32,648 --> 00:20:37,361
for his right to have babies
when he can't have babies?

424
00:20:37,403 --> 00:20:41,532
