against reality.

426
00:20:44,994 --> 00:20:48,330
[fanfare plays]

427
00:20:48,372 --> 00:20:52,459
[light applause]

428
00:20:52,501 --> 00:20:55,213
-[man] Get out there. Get out.
-[man #2] It's dangerous
out there.

429
00:20:55,254 --> 00:20:57,715
-[grunts]
-[applause]

430
00:21:07,433 --> 00:21:09,560
