-Haven't got any nuts, sorry.

436
00:21:24,158 --> 00:21:25,743
I've got wrens' livers,
badgers' spleens--

437
00:21:25,785 --> 00:21:27,703
No, no, no.

438
00:21:27,745 --> 00:21:30,414
-Otters' noses?
-I don't want any
of that Roman rubbish.

439
00:21:30,456 --> 00:21:33,500
-Why don't you sell proper food?
-Proper food?

440
00:21:33,542 --> 00:21:36,336
Yeah, not those rich
imperialist tidbits.

441
00:21:36,378 --> 00:21:39,590
Well, don't blame me.
I didn't ask to sell this stuff.

442
00:21:39,632 --> 00:21:41,634
All right, bag of
otters' noses, then.

443
00:21:41,675 --> 00:21:43,552
