454
00:22:07,618 --> 00:22:08,786
Shh, shh, shh!

455
00:22:09,870 --> 00:22:11,289
Are you sure?

456
00:22:11,330 --> 00:22:14,292
Oh, dead sure.
I hate the Romans already.

457
00:22:14,333 --> 00:22:17,837
Listen, if you wanted
to join the PFJ,

458
00:22:17,878 --> 00:22:20,798
