461
00:22:24,718 --> 00:22:26,344
A lot.

462
00:22:28,346 --> 00:22:30,224
Right, you're in.

463
00:22:30,266 --> 00:22:33,311
Listen, the only people
we hate more than the Romans

464
00:22:33,351 --> 00:22:35,313
are the fuckin'
Judean People's Front.

465
00:22:35,353 --> 00:22:36,772
-Yeah!
-Splitters.

466
00:22:36,814 --> 00:22:38,356
