01:23:35,552 --> 01:23:39,014
-And Swedish
separate from Welsh!
-[all grumbling]

1636
01:23:39,055 --> 01:23:42,893
All right, all right, all right!
We'll soon settle this!

1637
01:23:42,935 --> 01:23:47,648
Hands up, all those who
don't want to be crucified here!

1638
01:23:47,690 --> 01:23:48,983
[all grunting]

1639
01:23:49,024 --> 01:23:50,567
Right! Next!

1640
01:23:50,609 --> 01:23:52,736
Uh, look, it's not my cross.

1641
01:23:52,778 --> 01:23:54,864
-What?
-Um, it's not my cross.

1642
01:23:54,905 --> 01:23:56,323
I was holding it for someone.

1643
01:23:56,365 --> 01:23:58,534
Just lie down,
I haven't got all day!

1644
01:23:58,575 --> 01:24:00,786
No, of course. Look,
I hate to make a fuss--

1645
01:24:00,828 --> 01:24:04,164
