1667
01:25:13,358 --> 01:25:14,777
Hello, sibling Brian.

1668
01:25:14,818 --> 01:25:16,904
Thank God you've come, Reg.

1669
01:25:16,946 --> 01:25:19,364
Um, yes, I think I should
point out first, Brian,
in all fairness,

1670
01:25:19,406 --> 01:25:21,491
that we are not, in fact,
the rescue committee.

1671
01:25:21,533 --> 01:25:24,244
However, I have been asked
to read the following
prepared statement

1672
01:25:24,286 --> 01:25:26,288
on behalf of the movement.

1673
01:25:26,329 --> 01:25:28,206
"We, the People's
Front of Judea,

1674
01:25:28,248 --> 01:25:30,125
brackets, officials,
end brackets,

1675
01:25:30,166 --> 01:25:32,461
do hereby convey
our sincere fraternal

1676
01:25:32,502 --> 01:25:34,630
