the PFJ," et cetera.

1686
01:25:59,113 --> 01:26:00,948
And I'd just like to add,
on a personal note,

1687
01:26:00,990 --> 01:26:04,284
my own admiration
for what you're doing for us,
Brian,

1688
01:26:04,326 --> 01:26:08,163
